data.description: Welcome to 5615 Ivan's Farm! This charming farmhouse offers a peaceful and relaxing retreat. With its spacious layout and modern amenities, this home is perfect for a comfortable stay. It features a study, four bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, ensuring plenty of space for everyone. The interior boasts a cozy living area, fully equipped kitchen, and comfortable bedrooms. What sets this home apart is that it still has a structure warranty through the builder, giving you peace of mind and added protection. Conveniently located near local attractions and amenities, 5615 Ivan's Farm is the ideal destination for your next getaway. Schedule a showing today!
